data.title: TEDxOttawa
data.meta_description: TED.com, home of TED Talks, is a global initiative about ideas worth spreading via TEDx, The Audacious Project, TED Books, TED Conferences, TED-Ed and more.
data.text:
TEDxOttawa was an all day event filled with amazing speakers and attendees from all walks of life.

We weaved several themes together: The power of children, music and art, the environment, journeys and technology.
